          <img height="5" src="images/spacer-pix.gif" width="10"/>
          <br/>
          Over 200 senior researchers across the United States have been supported by the Interagency Education Research Initiative 
                (IERI) to learn the conditions 
                under which exemplary educational interventions improve student 
                learning outcomes in reading, mathematics, and science. The
          <a href="community/main.php">
           IERI 
                Research Community
          </a>
          zone on this website is designed to introduce 
                you to their projects and their findings. You can  also click on the brochure to the right to get
          <em>
           <a href="extra/just-the-facts.pdf">
            Just the Facts
           </a>
           .
          </em>
         </p>
         <p>
          If you are already a member 
                  of the IERI community, this is your portal to an extranet of information 
                  and resources about and from your IERI colleagues.
          <br/>
         </p>
