        <td class="text" width="96%">
         <p>
          <img height="5" src="images/spacer-pix.gif" width="200"/>
          <br/>
          The Data Research and Development Center (DRDC) is a research and 
            technical center funded by the U.S. Federal Government’s
          <a href="about/drdc_ieri.html">
           Interagency 
              Education Research Initiative
          </a>
          . As a research center, we work 
              to understand the factors that are essential for scaling-up promising 
              educational models, programs, and strategies. As a technical center, 
              we work to identify – and develop plans to address – the methodological and other challenges that arise when conducting 
              research on scaling.
         </p>
        </td>
