          <br/>
          DRDC conducts research that complements its technical support and capacity building missions.
          <a href="what/research.html">
           Click here
          </a>
          to learn more about the range of topics studied and resources produced.
         </p>
         <p>
          DRDC PI Barbara Schneider addressed the 2008 NSF ITEST Summit on prerequisites for scaling-up initiatives to kindle a STEM workforce.
          <a href="what/research_itest2008.html">
           Click here
          </a>
          to read her presentation and learn more about ITEST.
         </p>
         <p>
          A set of guidelines for using video in education research is now available.
          <a href="what/video-research.html">
           Click here
          </a>
          to access this report from a meeting hosted by DRDC.
         </p>
         <p>
          DRDC recently published the two-volume
          <em>
           Scale-Up in Education
          </em>
          (2007).
